A resident from Lunyara village at Maard at Majengo Ward in NkasiDistrict ,Rukwa region , MussaKapilima (17) died on the spot  while playing football after being  struck by lightning on Sunday evening . The Nkasi District Commissioner (DC), Mr Said Mtanda confirmed the  happening of incident that  it occurred on  Sunday evening at around 5:00 pm while the boy was playing with his age mates at Lunyara Primary School playing ground .  Across section of citizens from the precinct who preferred anonymity  associate the incident of lightning  with superstitious belief wondering why  was only  deceased boy was only picked among the  other 20 boys who were playing together  at the school football ground . 